java.lang.Object
dev.riko.golftourplanner.pathfinding.Dijkstra

public class Dijkstra extends Object implements GraphUtilFunctions<Dijkstra.Node>, Container
Dijkstra class that implements GraphUtilFunctions and Container interfaces for calculating the shortest path between two places in a world.
